e\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Lake House (film)|The Lake House]]''\n| Simon Wyler\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2007\n| ''[[Man in the Chair]]''\n| Flash Madden\n|[[Method Fest Independent Film Festival|Method Fest Award for Best Ensemble Cast]]\n|-\n| ''[[Closing the Ring]]''\n| Jack Etty\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Emotional Arithmetic]]''\n| David Winters\n|Nominated - [[Genie Award for Best Performance by an Actor in a Leading Role|Genie Award for Best Actor in a Leading Role]]\n|-\n| ''[[Already Dead]]''\n| Dr. Heller\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2009\n| ''[[Caesar and Cleopatra (play)|Caesar and Cleopatra]]''\n| [[Julius Caesar]]\n| Also executive producer\n|-\n| ''[[Up (2009 film)|Up]]''\n| Charles Muntz (voice)<ref name=\"btva\" />\n|\n|-\n| ''[[My Dog Tulip]]''\n| J.R. Ackerley (voice)<ref name=\"btva\" />\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Last Station]]''\n|[[Leo Tolstoy]]\n|Nominated - [[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br>Nominated - [[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br>Nominated - [[Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Male]]<br>Nominated - [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Supporting Role|SAG Award for Outstanding Male Performance in a Supporting Role]]\n|-\n|''[[9 (2009 animated film)|9]]''\n| 1 (voice)<ref name=\"btva\" />\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Imaginarium of Doctor Parnassus]]''\n| Doctor Parnassus\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Beginners]]''\n| Hal Fields\n|[[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br>[[BAFTA Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role]]<br>[[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br>[[Dorian Awards|Dorian Award for Film Performance of the Year]]<br>[[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor]]<br>Gold Derby Award for Best Supporting Actor<br>[[Gotham Awards|Gotham Award for Best Ensemble Performance]]<br>[[Hollywood Film Awards|Hollywood Film Award for Supporting Act